projects.title: NSC Events
projects.about: North Seattle College (NSC) provides a dynamic range of opportunities for students seeking engagement in campus life. This encompasses a diverse selection of events sponsored by Student Leadership and faculty, encompassing both entertaining and informative gatherings. Additionally, students can participate in thought-provoking lectures, community meetings, captivating library exhibits, and events tailored for transfer students.
